## 6. Notes on Implementation Readiness\
\
This design is intentionally "Part 2 ready, Part 3 friendly":\
- it keeps the schema simple enough to implement quickly;\
- it includes explicit index support for all six required queries;\
- it isolates complex booking-window logic into reusable code so we can test it independently;\
- and it avoids irreversible over-denormalization early in the project.\
\
If we observe bottlenecks in Part 3, the first tuning step would be precomputing monthly availability segments into a derived collection (materialized view style) to speed up queries 3 and 4.\
